{"tid":1480513,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"818，818，818，818，818，818湯渣華我屌你老母祖宗十八代","createTime":"2019-08-17T10:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T13:38:32.000Z","uid":201732,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"20f880c4a54b12dbd390746f7d85535afcb724b1","tid":1480513,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T10:40:32.000Z","msg":"818，818，818，818，818，818，818，818，818，818，818，818，818，818，818，818，818，818<br />\n<br />\n湯渣華而家VIU話暫緩同壽終正寢已經係好大退讓我屌你老母祖宗十八代<br />\n<br />\n林鄭唔撤回即係佢死不認錯呀<br />\n<br />\n人地波多黎各總統懷疑有岐視，出黎遊行佢都即刻落呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"150f8ad86666b416b1f09160201f989b0d1cde7f","tid":1480513,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T10:41:34.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n可以賽後檢討，但<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>It is now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hrJrLgG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhrJrLgG.jpg&h=d354981c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GMZbbWG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGMZbbWG.jpg&h=b5e6b6ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68c73153fa802f42337fcf89563c4d3a3d9384c2","tid":1480513,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T10:45:38.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母祖宗十八代"},{"pid":"ce6468f43ca345ecf81e488c8724e5b9fcdb1332","tid":1480513,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:09:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">818 和理非 着黑衫 帶gear 保護自己 砂布封右眼</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">完左遊行入機場</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n入嚟拎大量長輩圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://l